  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create 4 motes of superheated flame that circle around you like mini satellites. As a bonus action on each of your turns, you can spend a mote, allowing you to make a ranged Ninjutsu attack, throwing it at a creature you can see within 30 feet. On a hit, target creature takes 3d8+3 Fire damage and must succeed a Constitution saving throw, being Burned on a failed save.</p><p>Once all motes have been expended this jutsu immediately ends. You can alternatively spend the motes created by this jutsu to fuel other Scorch Release jutsu you cast, enhancing their effects.</p>",
